CSE 305 Project

src -> main -> webapp -> WEB-INF ->spring = Spring config
src -> main -> webapp -> WEB-INF ->views = JSP files - View
src -> main -> resources = logger
src -> main -> resources -> root-context.xml = configuration of java beans and mapping
src -> main -> java -> com.teamusa.app -> App.java = testing application 
src -> main -> java -> com.teamusa.controller -> HomeController.java = Mapping controller - Controllers 
src -> main -> java -> com.teamusa.dao -> CustomerDAO.java = interface for the JDBC class
src -> main -> java -> com.teamusa.dao.impl -> JdbcCustomerDAO.java = Configuration of SQL server and project - Model

